Limitations

The dataset contains content metadata only and does not include:

Customer information
Viewing history
Subscription details
Revenue or financial data
Transaction records

Therefore, Cohort Analysis, RFM Analysis, and Revenue Analysis were intentionally excluded because they are not supported by the available data.


